General.Name: A SPAC II Acquisition Corp. Ordinary Shares
General.Description: A SPAC II Acquisition Corp. does not have significant operations. The company focuses on effecting a merger, share exchange, asset acquisition, share purchase, reorganization, or similar business combination with one or more businesses. It intends to pursue prospective targets that are in the industries that apply technologies, such as Proptech and Fintech in North America, Europe, and Asia. The company was incorporated in 2021 and is based in Singapore. A SPAC II Acquisition Corporation operates as a subsidiary of A SPAC II (Holdings) Corp.
